Each layer of the application should use integration tests.
There is builtin test runner that you can use like this:


#[test]
fn integration() -> test_runner::Result {
    test_runner::test_snapshots("docs/", "<extension>", |input, _deps| {
        function that takes input: &str and returns String
    })
}

It runs markdown files like `docs/log.md` and finds every codeblock with the same <extension> as requested.

After making a change ALWAYS make sure everything passes by using `cargo xtask ci`. It will run clippy, format, tests, tree sitter codegen etc.
